==Awards and Honors==
* [[Jack Armstrong (baseball player)|Jack Armstrong]], [[Pitcher of the Month]] Award, May
* [[Rob Dibble]], Relief Pitcher and [[Randy Myers]], Relief Pitcher, NLCS MVP
* [[Billy Hatcher (baseball)|Billy Hatcher]], Outfield, [[Babe Ruth Award]]
* Billy Hatcher, Highest Batting Average in a World Series <ref>Great Baseball Feats, Facts and Figures, 2008 Edition, p.366, David Nemec and Scott Flatow, A Signet Book, Penguin Group, New York, NY, ISBN 978-0-451-22363-0</ref>
* [[Barry Larkin]], Shortstop, National League [[Silver Slugger]] Award
* [[Jose Rijo]], Pitcher, World Series MVP

'''[[1990 Major League Baseball All-Star Game|All-Star Game]]'''
* [[Jack Armstrong (baseball player)|Jack Armstrong]], Pitcher, Starter
* [[Chris Sabo]], Third Base, Starter

* [[Rob Dibble]], Relief Pitcher, Reserve
* [[Barry Larkin]], Shortstop, Reserve
* [[Randy Myers]], Relief Pitcher, Reserve

